---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Tools
description: Practical calculators and utilities from Sunset Guardian.
navKey: tools
---

<section class="page-hero page-hero-compact">
    <p class="eyebrow">Tools</p>

    <h1>Financial calculators without the clutter.</h1>

    <p class="hero-copy">
        Fast, straightforward tools that update instantly and require no
        account or login.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="section section-first">
    {% if collections.tools.length %}
        <div class="card-grid">
            {% for tool in collections.tools %}
                <a class="link-card" href="{{ tool.url }}">
                    <h2>{{ tool.data.title }}</h2>

                    <p>
                        {{ tool.data.description }}
                    </p>

                    <span>Open tool →</span>
                </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    {% else %}
        <div class="content-card empty-state">
            <h2>Tools are coming soon</h2>
            <p>Published calculators will appear here automatically.</p>
        </div>
    {% endif %}
</section>
